### Notification API Smoke Tests

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@userToken = mock-1001-USER

### 1. Get notification list
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications?page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### Expected Wave 1 content[] examples:
### - order_status with actionUrl /app/orders/{orderId}
### - support_ticket with actionUrl /app/support?ticketId={ticketId}
### - mediation_update with actionUrl /app/orders/{orderId}

### 2. Get unread notification count
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/unread-count
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### 3. Mark one notification read
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/1/read
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### 4. Mark all notifications read
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/read-all
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
